name: Nipple Penetration
description:
It's still a little crude. Has a few quirks that I'm patching.
Results vary wildly depending on the underlying checkpoint.

Success rate is about 20% currently, the other 80% are cronenburg abominations.


set the lora to 0.5 to start and increase until you are satisfied with the result. Some checkpoints need a higher value than others.
Works the best with kotosmix_v10 and HenmixRealV10

Try the different trigger words, it can be a little stubborn but sometimes they really change it up.

Some bugs that I still need to fix

  2. It sometimes makes too many nipples

  3. can turn limbs into boobs
